FT  10 MAY 94 / Cheers greet president Mandela
South African president Nelson Mandela embraces Inkatha leader Chief
Mangosuthu Buthelezi in the legislative chamber where the newly elected
parliament chose the African National Congress leader as the country's first
black head of state. Shares on the Johannesburg stock exchange welcomed the
event with a 2.5 per cent rise.
Report, Page 18
